	 noremap    <buffer>  <silent>  <LocalLeader>cl         :call Perl_EndOfLineComment()<CR>
	inoremap    <buffer>  <silent>  <LocalLeader>cl    <C-C>:call Perl_EndOfLineComment()<CR>
